[At this time there appears to be an improvement in the CFR from 50
percent to 34 percent. Taking the day of the week for each new
confirmation date gives us: Monday (3); Tuesday (1); Wednesday (0);
Thursday (4); and Friday (5) -- suggesting that the commonest days
for acquiring infection might be during the weekend 8 to 11 days or
so before the confirmation date. The last HPS press release was
issued on 22 Feb 2010. - Mod.MHJ]
